review:
>Amazing game!!!! I love her more than my mother ^_^
>I spend many hours in it. How much I played it in my childhood as a pirate-I can not count! You create a character and do whatever you want with his or her help! Open city unlike all numbered parts. There are a couple of flaws, but I think the developers will fix them all when they want...
>In other things, it's not so bad. If you dig into the game files and put a couple of mods, it will be candy. I discovered so much of the beauty of the game when I fixed and improved the game with mods. Thank you developers for letting me repair your game. After all, this is what we, ordinary players, wanted.
>Positive: 20 of DLC's for $20; Lags and friezes; 
>Negative: the game is not broken enough to quit; very addictive;
>This is the best experience in your life!!! Please link the game to Origins!!!!

